=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\t\twindow.google_analytics_uacct = \"UA-3380984-8\";\n</script>\n<div class=\"adsense\">\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\n\t\tgoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-7088061744296615\";\n\t\t/* CrawlWiki skyscraper */\n\t\tgoogle_ad_slot = \"8196155564\";\n\t\tgoogle_ad_width = 160;\n\t\tgoogle_ad_height = 600;\n-->\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n\t\t\t<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Storm bow</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From CrawlWiki</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\" class=\"mw-jump\">\n\t\t\t\t\tJump to:\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#mw-head\">navigation</a>, \t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#p-search\">search</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"border: 1px solid #33FF66; background-color: #e0fae0; border-left: 15px solid #33FF66; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Version <a href=\"/0.31\" title=\"0.31\">0.31</a></b>: This article <b>may not be</b> up to date for the <a href=\"/0.32\" title=\"0.32\">latest stable release</a> of Crawl.</i></div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> A longbow with the colour of dark rain clouds that fires arrows like lightning.\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><a href=\"/File:Longbow_storm_bow.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Longbow storm bow.png\" src=\"/images/7/7c/Longbow_storm_bow.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <i><b>the +8 storm bow</b></i>\n</p><p>+8 <a href=\"/Longbow\" title=\"Longbow\">longbow</a>\n</p><p><a href=\"/Electrocution\" title=\"Electrocution\">Electrocution</a> brand<br />\n<a href=\"/Penetration\" title=\"Penetration\">Penetration</a> brand\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Desirability\">Desirability</span></h2>\n<p>The <b>storm bow</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, as a +8 longbow of electrocution, is already a great item for <a href=\"/Ranged_Weapons\" title=\"Ranged Weapons\">Ranged Weapons</a> users (even if it takes a hefty skill investment). The added penetration allows it to shine in corridors, where only 1 enemy may hit you, but you get to hit multiple enemies for full damage. It also lets you snipe backline enemies without using <a href=\"/Dimensional_Bullseye\" title=\"Dimensional Bullseye\">Dimensional Bullseye</a>. While a longbow or <a href=\"/Triple_crossbow\" title=\"Triple crossbow\">triple crossbow</a> of a different brand may be stronger against rElec enemies, the penetration can make this bow worth using as a swapout.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>In <a href=\"/0.24\" title=\"0.24\">0.24</a>, the storm bow gained the penetration brand.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.23\" title=\"0.23\">0.23</a>, the storm bow would occasionally create rain <a href=\"/Cloud\" title=\"Cloud\">clouds</a> around the wielder, which could turn normal terrain into shallow <a href=\"/Water\" title=\"Water\">water</a> and shallow water into deep water for up to 100 turns.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <sp